

**Mamtsh g Jesus am i dagito Pilate wui **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:1-2, 11-14; Mark 15:1-5; John 18:28-38 *

1 Kutsh wehsijj hegam hahaꞌichu ab si e wehmt k am i bei g Jesus heg wui mash d kownal am Judea chekshani ch ed ch hab chehgig Pilate. 2 Sh ab ha kaiham. Kush ab wui ab haꞌichu abchudahim g Jesus hab kaijch, “Neh, ihda oꞌodham o im hu hab wabsh i ha wawan g t‑hemajkamga hab ha ahgch mat pi wo namkid g geꞌe kownal. Kuch kah mo hab hejel e ahg mo d jiosh si Kehsha ch d uhg kownal. Kupt hemho wa wo mua.” 

3 Kush ab kakke g Pilate g Jesus ch hab kaij, “Nap d ha‑kownalig g Tutuligo hemajkam?” 

Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Dani ahni.” 

4 Tsh g Pilate am i mamche hegai mam ab abchud. Sh eda muꞌi an oiopo g hemajkam s‑neidamk mo has e wua. Tsh g Pilate am ha kaichudk hab ha ah g uꞌugchu papal, “Pi ant haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh mas pi ap hab juh ihda oꞌodham mat heg hekaj wo e muhkid.” 

5 Kush wabshaba baꞌich i e gewpkad ch hab kaij, “Am o ha chuꞌamun g t‑wehm oꞌodham haꞌichu ha mashchamch wehsko ga hu Galilee t amjed ch ia Judea ch ed ch chum hems iia Jerusalem ch ed.” 

**Mamtsh am uꞌapa g jesus Herod wui **

6 Tsh am i kah g Pilate ihda k hab kaij ab ha wui, “Kutp ab Galilee chekshani ch ed d kihkam ihda oꞌodham?” 7 Kumsh am ahgid mash am haꞌab d kihkam. Sh g Herod am d ha‑kownalig Galilee chekshani ch ed ch iaꞌi idani am hab waꞌap haꞌichug Jerusalem t am. Kumtsh heg hekaj am wui uꞌapa g Jesus. 

8 Kush si s‑hehgig g Herod nash pi tash waꞌi chum s‑neidamk hab chum e ahgch matp hems am tahgio hab wo juh g s‑hasig haꞌichu. 9 Kumtsh am kei tahgio. Kush muꞌi haꞌichu kakke. Sh wabshaba pi has shaꞌi kaij g Jesus. 10 Kush g uꞌugchu papal ch chehanig ha mashchamdam am gegok ch si s‑gewkam ab haꞌichu abchud g Jesus. 11 Sh g Herod g e‑shondalig ha wehm haha wabsh nahnko ahg g Jesus ch si ash k ash g si s‑kehg kahba ab wahki. Tsh ab hahawa ha cheha g Herod mat wo uhpam bei am Pilate wui. 12 Kutsh heg i tash ab g Pilate ch Herod ab hahawa e nawojt k ash eda chum s‑e kehꞌid. 

**Mamtsh am i apꞌech matsh wo e muhkid g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:15-26; Mark 15:6-15; John 18:39–19:16 *

13 Tsh g Pilate am i ha hemapai g uꞌugchu papal ch ha wanimeddam g hemajkam 14 k ash hab kaij ab ha wui, “Ia amt uꞌapa ihda oꞌodham ni‑wui hab kaijch mo goꞌolko ha wanimed g hemajkam. Kunt hemuch ia em‑kaichudk am i mamche hegai mam ab abchud k pi haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh mas pi ap hab junihi m. 15 Kutsh Herod hab waꞌap pi haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh. T g shondaligaj ab uhpam i uꞌapa t‑wui. Pi atki haꞌichu hab juh ihda mas heg hekaj wo e muhkid. 16 Kunt wabsh wo ha cheha mat wo gewittan k wo dagito.” \[ 17 Neh, bash kaij nash pi am hema i dadagitosh g lihso ha wehhejed wehs ahid ab mo eda hab e wua hegai geꞌe gegosig.\] 

18 Kush wehsijj hegam muꞌi hemajkam mo am haꞌichug si s‑kaidam hab kaij, “Pi ach tatchua ihda. Barabbas apt wo i dagito t‑wehhejed.” 19 Sh eda ihda Barabbas am e kuhpch nash pi chum haꞌi ha wehm cheggia g kownal ch haꞌi ha kokda. 

20 Sh am ep chum ha wehm neok g Pilate nash pi chum s‑dagitoimk g jesus. 21 Sh wabshaba am ep si s‑kaidam hab ge kaij muꞌikko, “Muꞌani\! Muꞌani ab kots t ab\!” 

22 Sh hab ep chum kaij g Pilate, “A t haschu pi ap hab juh. Pi ant haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh mas heg hekaj wo e muhkid. Ab ant wo ha cheha mat wo gewittan k wo dagito.” 

23 Sh wabshaba am wabsh si s‑kaidam hab kaij matsh ab wo naggia kots t ab. Neh, tsh g ha‑hihinki gewito g Pilate. 24 Tsh am i apꞌech mat am hab wo e juh g ha‑tatchui. 25 Kumtsh gam hu i wuhshad hegai mash d ha cheggiadkam ch d ha muꞌakam k amtsh g Jesus am i dagito ha wui mat am hab wo juh mo has i elid. 

**Mamtsh ab naggia g Jesus kots t ab **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:32-44; Mark 15:21-32; John 19:17-27 *

26 Kumtsh gam hu i bei g Jesus ab kushwiotachudk g kots. Kush am hu hebai hihim. Tsh ab hema i ha nam g oꞌodham mash ab him Jerusalem wui. Id ash hab chehgig Simon ch ab d kihkam mash am d Cyrene ch ash ab him ga hu oꞌoidag amjed. Kumtsh am wabsh si be k ab kushwiotach g kots k atsh hab juh mat ab oidk wo himad g Jesus. 

27 Kush muꞌi hemajkam ab oidch hihim. Sh g uꞌuwi si shoanihim wehhejed. 28 Tsh ab i ha nei g Jesus k hab kaij ab ha wui, “Pi g am ni‑wehhejed wo shoanid, ahpim Jerusalem t am kihkam, ch wabshaba hejel e wehhejed ch e‑aꞌaliga ha wehhejed. 29 Ab o him g tash mat hab wo chei g hemajkam mo si haꞌichu s‑ha abamk hegam uꞌuwi mat pi hekid shaꞌi mahmadt. 30-31 Woho o wa mat s‑ta ehbidam haꞌichu hab wo e juh am ni‑tahgio. T wabshaba baꞌich i s‑ta ehbidam haꞌichu hab haha wo juh am ha tahgio hegam mo d pi ap chuꞌijkam ch pi ab hu ni‑wui e nohnogimk. \(30\) Hegam at pi wo e nako mas heg wo nako k heg hekaj wo chum tatchua mat g dohdaꞌag am ha dahm wo i shulig k wo ha ehsto.” 

32 Kumsh gohk ep ha uꞌa mamtsh am wehmaj wo ha kokda. Sh idam d pi ap hehemajkam. 33 Kumtsh an dada anai mash am hab e aꞌaga Koshwak. Tsh g shondal ab hahawa sisish g Jesus kots t ab k am i kei g kots wag ch ed k gan hu aꞌai hab waꞌap ha nahngia hegam pi ap hehemajkam kokots t ab. 

34 Tsh ab hahawa e hoꞌigeꞌidahu g Jesus k hab kaij, “Ni‑ohg Jiosh, ab g wabsh si i s‑ha hoꞌigeꞌid hegam mat ab ni‑naggia. Pi o shaꞌi mahch mani d si m‑Kehsha ch d s‑apꞌekam.” 

Kutsh g shondal am e chichwi k g wehschugaj e toꞌi. 

35 Sh g hemajkam am gegok ch neid wehs ihda. Sh g ha wanimeddam nahnko ahg g Jesus ch hab kaij, “Ha at doꞌibia haꞌi, pegih, k hejel wo e doꞌibia matp d Jiosh si Kehsha.” 

36 Kush g shondal hab waꞌap nahnko wua ch hab wabsh s‑junim k ab chum mah g nawait 37 ch wabsh nahnko ahg hab kaijch, “Oi g hejel e doꞌibiad napsh pi d ge kownal.” 

38 Sh am dahm oꞌohadag ihda, “Id o d Tutuligo hemajkam ha‑kownalig.” 

39 Kush hema hegam pi ap hehemajkam mash ab hab waꞌap naggia kots t ab ab si s‑koꞌokam has ahg g Jesus ch hab kaij, “Neh, kuptp d ge Jiosh si Kehsha, pegih, k wo hejel e doꞌibia k ahchim ep wo t‑doꞌibia.” 

40 Kush g hema ab si s‑kehꞌid ihda ch hab kaij, “Aha nap pi ehbid g Jiosh. Ia ach t‑wehm nahngia ch ab t‑wepo mohtoꞌidas g chuꞌijig. 41 Kuch ahchim s‑ap ab mohtoꞌidas nach pi wa woho d pi ap chuꞌijkam. Kutsh eda ihda pi hab shaꞌi juh g pi apꞌekam.” 

42 Neh, bash kaij ihda hema ch ab Jesus wui hab hahawa ep kaij, “Jesus, ab apt wo wa al s‑ni‑chegitok hekid ab bek g e‑kownaltalig.” 

43 Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Neh, ni ab si m‑ahgid mapt id i tashkaj wo ni‑wehmajk an Jiosh kihdag ed.” 

**Matsh muh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:45-56; Mark 15:33-41; John 19:28-30 *

44 Kutsh am i dahm juh. Tsh muh g tash k wehsko s‑chuhugam ch ab ai g waik ohla. 45 Kutsh am geꞌe cheopi ch ed g s‑kowk ikus kuhpadag ab si shel e wantsh. 46 Kush am si s‑kaidam e hoꞌigeꞌidahun g Jesus Jiosh wui ch hab kaij, “Ni‑ohg, ab ant i m‑mah g ni‑doakag.” Neh, bash cheꞌiok am i muh. 

47 Kutsh am i nei g shondal ha‑geꞌejig matsh haschu has e juh k ab si ihm g Jiosh ch hab kaij, “Woho oki d s‑apꞌekam oꞌodham ihda.” 

48 Tsh amjed muꞌijj gam hu uhpam hihi hegam mash ab neid ab wabsh e wecho wahpkch nash pi oi wa si ap e tatat. 49 Kush wehsijj hegam mo si s‑mahch g Jesus ga hu wabsh mehk gegok ch ab neid wehs ihda. Haꞌi idam ash d hegam uꞌuwi mash ga hu Galilee t amjed an wehmajkahim g Jesus. 

**Mamtsh ged hu cheh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:57-61; Mark 15:42-47; John 19:38-42 *

50-51 Sh eda wa hema hegam e jehnigiddam chum pi hohhoꞌid matsh g wehmaj e jehnigiddam s‑muꞌam k ah g Jesus. Id ash hab chehgig Joseph ch ab d kihkam mash am d Arimathea ch s‑ap d oꞌodham ch ab nenida g Jiosh kownaltalig. 52 Tsh hekid am i muh g Jesus, tsh ha hekaj am wui hih g Pilate k ab si e shoꞌigchud k tahni g honshpadaj. Tsh am wa apꞌech matsh wo bei. 53 Tsh gam hu ep him k ab i huduni. Sh am mia hab chuꞌig g hihaꞌini ch ab heki hu cheotas hodai ch ed ch pi koi e hekaj. Tsh g Joseph am i bei g honshpadag k ged hu heg eda cheh am i hobinodk g s‑kehg ikuskaj. 

54-55 Tsh hegam uꞌuwi mo wehmajkahim g Jesus ab Galilee t amjed gam hu oi g Joseph k ash neid mat hebai e cheh g Jesus k has masma ab e woi. \(54\) Kush d wialos. Sh g hemajkam chum e nakog no pi g shahwai d ha‑mihshmda tash. 56 Kutsh gam hu uhpam hihi idam uꞌuwi mash hebai dadha k am i apꞌech haꞌichu mat hekaj wo s‑ap hab juh mo hab masma hab ha wua g e‑koꞌidag k ash am hahawa e ulinihogi mihshmda tash ch ed mo hab masma d ha‑chehanig. 

